JXLS template for Electricity Invoice
This is a binary XLSX file template.
The actual template should be created in Excel with JXLS markup comments:
jx:area(lastCell="L15")

Key cells with JXLS markup:
A2: ${invoice.invoiceTitle} (فاتورة كهرباء)
C2: ${invoice.areaName}
C3: ${invoice.projectName}
C4: ${invoice.unitNumber}
F4: ${invoice.invoiceNumber}
A6: ${invoice.meterType}
B6: ${invoice.customerCode}
C6: ${invoice.issueDate}
E6: ${invoice.billingPeriod}
G6: ${invoice.meterSerial}
K6: ${invoice.companyLicense}
A8: عدد العددات
B8: السيد/
K8: ${invoice.currentReading}
L8: قراءة عداد
A10: مقابل القدرة
B10: العنوان/
K10: ${invoice.previousReading}
A12: خصومات (جم)
B12: ${invoice.discountAmount}
D12: ${invoice.settlementAmount}
F12: ${invoice.stampFees}
H12: ${invoice.consumptionValue}
K12: ${invoice.consumptionUnits}
L12: ${invoice.customerServiceFees}
A14: ${invoice.totalLabel}
B14: ${invoice.amountInWords}
L14: ${invoice.totalLabel}
A15: ${invoice.totalAmount}
K17: ${invoice.signatureLabel}

JXLS commands:
jx:forEach(items="invoices" var="invoice" lastCell="L17" on="electricity")
